    "body" : "Thing is, if you try java.exe, you will need to set classpath, which is a nightmare. But the classpath is already available in pom.xml or gradle.build. So Maven and Gradle provide plugin(maven)/task(gradle) to run and do the heavy lifting for you. mvn:spring-boot run, and ./gradlew bootRun."
