      "body" : "You can simplify that command by adding &quot;fully qualified Main class name in pom.xml&quot;. Example: &lt;plugin&gt;                 &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;                 &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-maven-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;                                  &lt;configuration&gt; \t                &lt;archive&gt; \t                    &lt;manifest&gt; \t                        &lt;mainClass&gt;com.myproject.myapp.Application&lt;/mainClass&gt; \t                    &lt;/manifest&gt; \t                &lt;/archive&gt; \t            &lt;/configuration&gt;             &lt;/plugin&gt;"
    }, {
