    "body" : "<p>Run Spring Boot app using Maven</p>\n<p>You can also use Maven plugin to run your Spring Boot app. Use the below example to run your Spring Boot app with Maven plugin:</p>\n<pre><code>mvn spring-boot:run\n</code></pre>\n<p>Run Spring Boot App with Gradle</p>\n<p>And if you use Gradle you can run the Spring Boot app with the following command:</p>\n<pre><code>gradle bootRun\n</code></pre>\n"
