    "body" : "<p>For macOS user\nIf you configured your application using <code>maven</code>\nFirst, go to your project directory in the terminal\nthen simply run</p>\n<pre><code>./mvnw spring-boot:run\n</code></pre>\n<p>You are done. Now you can hit localhost with port number.</p>\n<p>This command mentioned in the <a href=\"https://spring.io/guides/gs/spring-boot/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">spring official guide</a>.</p>\n"
